      {
        "question": "Which platforms support Hive Mind?",
        "answer": "Hive Mind works with Claude, Codex, and Claude Code through Task command generation and direct CLI execution via npx claude-flow."
      },
      {
        "question": "What are the memory limits?",
        "answer": "Default memory is 100MB with 1000 cache entries. Configurable up to higher limits with compression and automatic garbage collection."
      },
      {
        "question": "How does Hive Mind integrate with existing workflows?",
        "answer": "Use npx claude-flow hive-mind spawn for CLI execution, or integrate programmatically through HiveMindCore API for custom implementations."
